cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically the use of recurrent neural networks for language modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses federated learning, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves privacy and security concerns, which could fall under the categories of cryptography (cs.CR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, since the focus is primarily on language modeling, cs.CL is the most likely category.
